headline: Transport Stocks Surge as Senate Passes Megabill
summary: Transportation stocks rose Tuesday after the Senate passed President Trump's tax-and-spending megabill on hopes the legislation could spur demand for trucking and other logistics services. The Dow Jones Transportation Average was up 3% mid-afternoon, led by Ryder System, up nearly 7%; J.
